# Trustim skill symlinks — recreated by `lab repo refresh-skills` on
# every `lab repo pull`. They use absolute paths into
# `repositories/trustim-investigation/skills/` so they're machine-
# specific and don't belong in the tree.
.claude/skills/investigation-*
